{"word":"G2727 - κατηχέω - katēchéō - kat-ay-kheh'-o - Inform","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατηχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>katēchéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kat-ay-kheh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Inform"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உபதேசி, போதி, பேசு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to sound toward, sound down upon, resound"},{"paragraph":"2. to teach orally, to instruct"},{"paragraph":"3. to inform by word of mouth"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G2279 - ἦχος - ēchos - ay'-khos/2279\">G2279</a>; to <i>sound down</i> into the ears, that is, (by implication) to <i>indoctrinate</i> (&ldquo;catechize&rdquo;) or (generally) to <i>apprise</i> of: - inform, instruct, teach."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}